query:
/*+  */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('algorithms',
'grammar',
'meaning',
'meaning-in-context',
'organic-chemistry',
'sentence-construction',
'word-usage')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 10
inner join badge AS b
on b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Citizen Patrol',
'Constituent',
'Curious',
'Enlightened',
'Good Answer',
'Good Question',
'Revival')
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = b.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('chemistry',
'cs',
'ell')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
